  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WELCOME TO HORROR NIGHT!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your way out from an abandoned mansion by solving puzzles, hiding from a horrifying creature, and working in team, in a new <i>multiplayer, third person, horror</i> experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiplayer Videogame</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape alongside your friends and <strong>don't let the creature catch them! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get rewarded by helping your teammates, solving puzzles and working in team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Revive all survivors by bringing their skulls into the resurrection ritual! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/3e61a4e151e406c1299d99f7c5e5bc1f.poster.avif?t=1756041243\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/3e61a4e151e406c1299d99f7c5e5bc1f.webm?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/3e61a4e151e406c1299d99f7c5e5bc1f.mp4?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play as the Creature</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your favorite skin, improve your skills by eating rats, and crouch for better speed <i>to catch all survivors.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt down every single one of them <i>to become winner!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve Puzzles to Escape the Mansion</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape by solving <i>randomized puzzles</i> in the mansion, or simply completing a hidden ritual that will get you out of the mansion. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Not all clues will lead to something]. <i>Teamwork is essential!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>As a Survivor:</i> Customize your character by choosing from a variety of hairstyles, outfits, accesories, lamps and much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>As the Monster:</i> Select the scariest skin to hunt all players down! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/e449916a9802c67aa772ebd14eb7ded5.poster.avif?t=1756041243\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/e449916a9802c67aa772ebd14eb7ded5.webm?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/e449916a9802c67aa772ebd14eb7ded5.mp4?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Progress</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new items by levelling up! (<i>You can also acquire them on the official Horror Night Store</i>)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/89a4d7338194b32dd17fad6ea3dcd483.poster.avif?t=1756041243\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/89a4d7338194b32dd17fad6ea3dcd483.webm?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/89a4d7338194b32dd17fad6ea3dcd483.mp4?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New Lobby</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Waiting for your friends to join a match is no longer tedious ;) You'll be able to explore much more terrifying surroundings while doing so, and even speed up the game by simply pressing the new \"force start match\" lever. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/ea3dd7add87ba717b1e32b6896077213.poster.avif?t=1756041243\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/ea3dd7add87ba717b1e32b6896077213.webm?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/ea3dd7add87ba717b1e32b6896077213.mp4?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><strong>Character Selection</strong></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the monster or as a survivor in this <i>Free to Play</i> asymmetric version, by throwing yourself into the <i>Well Of Doom</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/415a02b6141fdca04d1665ae0726e389.poster.avif?t=1756041243\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/415a02b6141fdca04d1665ae0726e389.webm?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/415a02b6141fdca04d1665ae0726e389.mp4?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Improved Interaction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interacting with objects is now faster and easier. Just by pressing E! ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/f5b719e66edcce6c27f8b142d5bb40df.poster.avif?t=1756041243\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/f5b719e66edcce6c27f8b142d5bb40df.webm?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/f5b719e66edcce6c27f8b142d5bb40df.mp4?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Teleportation</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape from the Ayurok clutches even faster through <i>portals and wardrobes. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New <i>Horror Night</i> Store</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire new items in the <i>official store,</i> by either shopping with real cash (buying gold coins), or simply by completing different missions and objectives within the game, to earn silver coins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WELCOME TO HORROR NIGHT!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your way out from an abandoned mansion by solving puzzles, hiding from a horrifying creature, and working in team, in a new <i>multiplayer, third person, horror</i> experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiplayer Videogame</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape alongside your friends and <strong>don't let the creature catch them! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get rewarded by helping your teammates, solving puzzles and working in team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Revive all survivors by bringing their skulls into the resurrection ritual! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/3e61a4e151e406c1299d99f7c5e5bc1f.poster.avif?t=1756041243\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/3e61a4e151e406c1299d99f7c5e5bc1f.webm?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/3e61a4e151e406c1299d99f7c5e5bc1f.mp4?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play as the Creature</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your favorite skin, improve your skills by eating rats, and crouch for better speed <i>to catch all survivors.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt down every single one of them <i>to become winner!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve Puzzles to Escape the Mansion</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape by solving <i>randomized puzzles</i> in the mans