p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Improved Interaction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interacting with objects is now faster and easier. Just by pressing E! ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/f5b719e66edcce6c27f8b142d5bb40df.poster.avif?t=1756041243\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/f5b719e66edcce6c27f8b142d5bb40df.webm?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721350/extras/f5b719e66edcce6c27f8b142d5bb40df.mp4?t=1756041243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Teleportation</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape from the Ayurok clutches even faster through <i>portals and wardrobes. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New <i>Horror Night</i> Store</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire new items in the <i>official store,</i> by either shopping with real cash (buying gold coins), or simply by completing different missions and objectives within the game, to earn silver coins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
